{"_id":"BEGEbZUAxmKCs1Sv","name":"Tips","content":"<h1>Tips</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Hero Pool</h2>\n<p>Token HUD Wildcard for Foundry VTT</p>\n<p>You can use Token HUD Wildcard to change tokens with numbers. Making clear the hero pool.</p>\n<p>https://github.com/javieros105/FVTT-TokenHUDWildcard</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>FoundryVTT - Party Resources</p>\n<p>You can use Party Resources to control the hero pool.</p>\n<p>https://github.com/davelens/fvtt-party-resources</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Theatre</h2>\n<p>Use Theatre to make the PCs feel in the scene.</p>\n<p>https://github.com/League-of-Foundry-Developers/fvtt-module-theatre</p>\n<p> </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JDmxZLk15dRViDS7","name":"Macros","content":"<h1>Macros</h1>\n<p>You have a macro to let your players change labels easier.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/commodities/treasure/mask-jeweled-gold.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Label Changer</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Import the macro to the world. </li>\n<li>Share it with your players.</li>\n<li>They must select their token. </li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/macro-labelchanger.png\" width=\"397\" height=\"334\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Notes</p>\n<p>The token must be linked to the actor.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"V88zf4vBGsTs30B7","name":"Templates","content":"<h1>Templates</h1>\n<p>Before anything you need to add a template to your world.</p>\n<p>Use this model: <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CyricPL/masks-newgeneration-unofficial-revised/main/templates/masks.txt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Link</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c9vS4ZyHtV2VjmN0","name":"How To Set Up CUB","content":"<h1>How To Set Up CUB</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<p>You can make the condition show on a token when the player mark it on the Actor Sheet with the module Combat Utility Belt.</p>\n<p>First you need to enable Condition Lab.</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks02.webp\" width=\"749\" height=\"454\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>You need to create a trigger On and Off to each condition.</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks01.webp\" width=\"800\" height=\"711\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>This is the values you can use for each condition:</p>\n<p>Afraid</p>\n<p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.0.value</p>\n<p>Angry </p>\n<p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.1.value</p>\n<p>Guilty </p>\n<p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.2.value</p>\n<p>Hopeless </p>\n<p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.3.value</p>\n<p>Insecure</p>\n<p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.4.value</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>You need to create the conditions. You can import then using this link: <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/brunocalado/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/main/resources/cub-pbta-condition-map.json\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Link</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks03.webp\" width=\"800\" height=\"477\" /></p>\n<p>Make sure each condition has its triggers defined.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Icons</h2>\n<p>Angry: icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp</p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Afraid: icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp</p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Guilty: icons/creatures/mammals/humanoid-cat-skulking-teal.webp</p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/creatures/mammals/humanoid-cat-skulking-teal.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Hopeless: icons/creatures/magical/spirit-undead-masked-blue.webp</p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/creatures/magical/spirit-undead-masked-blue.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Insecure: icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp</p>\n<p><img src=\"icons/magic/death/undead-skeleton-deformed-red.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PIYJckcNzA7ukurN":3},"flags":{}}
